00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:05.000
Blake Lively, one of the major characters of sitcom Gossip Girl,

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:10.000
has accepted the role of Elisabeth Bennet in Pride and Prejudice.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:14.000
The same role wasn't accepted by Scarlett Johansson and Emma Stone.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:18.000
Lively has been very busy also with Ben Affleck's film,

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:19.000
The Town, and Green Lantern.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:26.000
The submission list for the 84th Annual Academy Awards

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:28.000
foreign-language category was updated.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:31.000
This year there are more then forty countries participating.

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:35.000
The list is composed by films like Wim Wender's “Pina” (Germany) and

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:38.000
Aki Karismaki's “Le Havre” (Finland),

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:42.000
which for the jury are very promising.

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:43.000
That’s all for today!

